body.name: Active Element Commercial Dishwasher Detergent - Active Element - Makes Two 5 Gallon Pail - Industrial Dish Detergent - For High and Low Temp Dishwasher Machine
features: Powerful cleaning action cuts through tough grease, grime and food stains leaving dishes looking brand new. Our Industrial dish detergent dissolves food soils and emulsifies fats in no time.
For use in both high temp and low temperature commercial dishwasher. The liquid machine dishwasher detergent is fed directly from 5-gallon pail during wash cycle.
Sold as concentrated powder that makes 5-gallons of powerful liquid detergent. Simply mix with water. Watch mixing video on step by step instructions. Pail not included.
Cost effective product shipped factory direct. For high temperature dishwasher detergent use with rinse aid. In low temp, use dish machine soap plus commercial dishwasher sanitizer and rinse aid.
Not for household use. Read and understand Safety Data Sheets before use including precautionary measures and personal protective equipment. Do not use on aluminum kitchen ware
body.description: Commercial Dishwasher Detergent Description Active Element's commercial-grade detergent contains powerful cleaning action that targets tough grease, grime and stains leaving dishes looking brand new. Great for any food service kitchen including restaurants, diners, hotels, schools and not-for-profits. Intended for use in both high and low commercial dishwashers with water temperature above 120 degrees Fahrenheit. Shipped as a concentrate, each unit (2-bottles) is diluted with water to make 5-gallons of powerful detergent (Pail is not included). Simply pour concentrate into empty 5-gallon pail. Fill pail with water. Apply label and ready for use. Mix in a well ventilated area or outdoors and avoid inhalation. Not for household use. Do not use on aluminum kitchen ware. Read and understand the SDS. The SDS provides description of hazards, precautions, personal protective equipment, first aid, 24-hour emergency contact, storage data and handling procedures.

Product Features Cuts through tough grease, grime and stains leaving dishes looking brand new. Commercial-Grade product for use in both high and low temperature dishwasher machines. Sold as concentrated powder that makes 5-gallons of powerful detergent. Pail not included. Cost effective product shipped factory direct. Not for household use. Do not use on aluminum kitchen ware.

How It Works Detergent Dosage The recommended detergent dosage is between 0.5-1 floz (1-2 tbsp) per gallon of water. The dosage level will be determined by several factors including incoming water hardness, water temperature, water consumption of the machine model, warewash soil loadings, and the number of cycles between draining of the wash tank.
